The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Narco ruling
                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                      Narco ruling
                            
	Jaipur, May 13: An Ajmer blast accused today became among the first beneficiaries of last weeks Supreme Court order that no person can be forced to undergo lie-detector tests, reports our correspondent.        
	A sessions court set aside the permission granted by a trial court for a narco test on Devender Gupta, arrested last month for the 2007 explosion near the dargah.                                                                                                                                                           
